===Etymology===
;to hunt
:{{w|Zheng Xuan}} (cited in {{zh-ref|Bodde, 1975}} & {{zh-ref|Schuessler, 2007}}) relates {{och-l|獵}} to {{och-l|臘}}, commenting that "''là'' [臘 (lɑp)] is a designation for the sacrifice made of animals which have been caught in a hunt ''liè'' (ljap)" [https://ctext.org/library.pl?if=gb&file=2246&page=40#%E8%87%98%E8%AC%82%E4%BB%A5%E7%94%B0%E7%8D%B5%E6%89%80%E5%BE%97%E7%A6%BD%E7%A5%AD%E4%B9%9F].
:See {{zh-l|*臘}} for etymology.

;turtle, tortoise
:From {{inh|zh|sit-pro|*k-lip||turtle, tortoise}} (STEDT, {{zh-ref|Schuessler, 2007}}). See there for cognates.

